{"tid":2108303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安局李家超故意輸入大量中國病人阻礙選舉進行","createTime":"2020-07-14T12:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T05:08:41.000Z","uid":26770,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8167ec6948c71a97748f8faa456384577f9dc216","tid":2108303,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"疫源好明顯係果堆'豁免在內地從事生產作業的香港企業接受強制檢疫安排的申請機制'<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/04/P2020050400335.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202005%2F04%2FP2020050400335.htm&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=c597923f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202005/04/P2020050400335.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n病毒唔會因為係黨企人員而唔感染,反而商界人士周圍去更容易奶野<br />\n而且中國貪污盛行,<ins> 關口已有人賣香港的免檢資格</ins><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2107638/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2107638/page/1</a><br />\n由pr公司行動反推<br />\n港共好驚35+與激進派在初選大勝<br />\n<ins>保安局李家超有動機輸入瘟疫</ins><br />\n------------------------------<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><strong>香港紀律部隊干犯反人類罪早有大量案例</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190909/7VHI3IOTE4XQOAEYESZBLFCECI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190909%2F7VHI3IOTE4XQOAEYESZBLFCECI%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=ec78c691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190909%2F7VHI3IOTE4XQOAEYESZBLFCECI%2F&h=5b38a871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190909/7VHI3IOTE4XQOAEYESZBLFCECI/</a><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">李家超視察新疆：反恐值得參考<br />\n同年大量女示威者遭警隊性侵犯與強姦</span><br />\n<br />\n懲教一哥胡英明係2019年2月頭已部署好酷刑迫害政治犯<br />\n引進監犯手環防止政治犯自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2005171/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2005171/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"b9b2a3a79f891efd29c96f65ee5fc90bc61347f9","tid":2108303,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76234bfcaff8b3c9b15b7b60f5b44d972352992b","tid":2108303,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6de80155e6fe48690a0e9c7a9d187e71a392c38","tid":2108303,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後叫班藍絲屈係71遊行搞到爆疫"},{"pid":"57dcd2fa5fa731fb7286f9bc522fefe22f147c0c","tid":2108303,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"比加超謀殺香港人"},{"pid":"3b727c3fe9601a96132582318928ba30e111173c","tid":2108303,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又想殺香港人"},{"pid":"585b804e681dca52621fecffc96a3a8ac999225d","tid":2108303,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c037cd0da0c44c78a40990673ddbf112c93590","tid":2108303,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"對方玩到打出瘟疫牌<br />\n故意輸入瘟疫係等於攪死香港經濟<br />\n<br />\n現在市況已經差, 玩手段累一堆公司摺埋係會影響埋其他公司的運作<br />\n例如:公司大客著草<br />\n------------------